幾時低?個恆指而家先係跌勢頭，你信三上二落走勢既話等二萬四之後再講。<br />\n<br />\n股市靠人托價，有人出得起價就有得升，唯一有得跌市賺就係各種PUT熊證反向期指同埋反向ETF。<br />\n<br />\n你新手又真係要入，建議你買7300個D，恆指越跌你越開心，又唔駛睇住到期，只係無上面講個D賺咁多。<br />\n<br />\n講等收息儲錢，唔係是但買就得，巨人都可以殞落，你先睇下公司對務靠唔靠得住先。"},{"pid":"706f31336eb652efc18a10cd7873a102e2350bfd","tid":729743,"uid":83602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"留名學下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c0e39959b193b4fdddb88d08bdcb91c92659e5","tid":729743,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"藍籌唔跌個個都扑住去買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed580955d02f4aa8e6e25c657872abd0ea2e361a","tid":729743,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"熊市買正股?"},{"pid":"c93b9ef08020d37a56684159361e37208f9360e4","tid":729743,"uid":109189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b23ba31fea666c06573a4c847341029905c84a0","tid":729743,"uid":27772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"唔好買籃籌 <br />\n真肺腑之言"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T08:49:37.000Z","msg":"望下29蚊買左吉利 依家仲未放果d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c8981a171aa648b02f95b35323249004bafb78","tid":729743,"uid":83594,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"大學生講岀藍籌唔會蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都係草埋d錢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d21798ab686aa4970e95f53bf86a0f948d7c81","tid":729743,"uid":11261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"1299<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa4405b3b3b4ef38b5a7377de6c1809bd422a94","tid":729743,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:05:24.000Z","msg":"175<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100d964b25b3138a8c51dea80de5e0325c1811cc","tid":729743,"uid":103926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0876458394b0ecdc69feed504d73e449da842e4","tid":729743,"uid":109189,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b0dac7d27645f777f096f97209f3c88ee27917b5","tid":729743,"uid":140590,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"b5872d4db0301cb5640fb5db93644fcec7a5c8ae","tid":729743,"uid":159531,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T22:50:49.000Z","msg":"首先，你要諗下自己既風險承受能力有幾高，講緊係你自己心理可以負擔得起跌幾多。如果你可以大起大落，本少可以去投機，買牛熊，不過你有好大機會蝕一大筆，因為基本上係賭市。<br />\n<br />\n問得買藍籌股就一定係想本少玩下，不過你唔好彩，宜家個市係最仆街難玩既時候，入市玩藍籌你可以預自己坐貨，即係有較大機會蝕本蝕時間。<br />\n<br />\n後生唔應該買藍籌正股，原因你本少，不過你時間多，但係你又要番學喎，咁點算<br />\n<br />\n買ETFS, 2800你本太少，你可以考慮買Blackrock 既3115又或者投資美國市場作指數投資3140。ETFs既基本原則係大市升，你升，大市跌，你跌。你唔洗自己操盤。<br />\n<br />\n入市要睇時機，宜家係咪？ 你要自己判斷。記住，你可以聽好多人既意見，但你一定要自己下判斷，因為錢係你揸手。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T23:10:09.000Z","msg":"藍籌唔係唔會蝕架咩？升跌極都有個譜<br />\n我屋企人話求其買隻銀行股擺係度等收息就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋想請教一下，所謂時機即係幾時先叫岩？以我皮毛既認知淨係識低價買入高價放岀既concept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似諗得太簡單，有無咩野方法去學投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T23:48:16.000Z","msg":"點解讀到大學都講得出有股票係唔會蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"其實真係有 當5號仔你平均70蚊入 升幾多跌幾多都唔放 <br />\n一年收返4蚊息 收十年即係賺40蚊息 成本30蚊 但十年後既5號仔 可能已經賣緊130了"},{"pid":"c2a07aee3d6659e22df60fce94fb9ca2200efdae","tid":729743,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:03:54.000Z","msg":"趁熊市你上網睇書做下功課先<br />\n本少都可以玩正股，最多坐幾年等佢牛市升翻<br />\n當然亦都可以玩衍生工具滾大佢，但有機會total loss<br />\n<br />\n牛=升，熊=跌<br />\netf 最出名就係盈富<br />\n<br />\n 新股叫IPO ，上市前認購，搏佢高開炒高左即放<br />\n當然你如果睇好佢，認購唔中都可以上市日即買，如：毛記 單日8.5-&gt;11"},{"pid":"ee7bc863366e3fb3fe1cfd87eb002ebbcfd10735","tid":729743,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"大學生賺得幾多個錢，拎黎溝女旅行發展興趣乜都好啦<br />\n之後搵份20~30k以上既工，幾皮野半年乜都賺得返又何必咁玩入股票市場呢?"},{"pid":"87234de908a395437eda78cc537ffbb56c5eff60","tid":729743,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f65b72b5c538481516c4f5f08a0d1759b83def6","tid":729743,"uid":69661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"低價買，高價賣，個個都知<br />\n但現實有幾多人做到？<br />\n有冇諗過高價入，更高價賣出？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大牛個陣既2382<br />\n趣趣地買一手正股<br />\n星期五142入星期五爆升10幾蚊個次<br />\n賺成千幾銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7da981d72042e705793d0d76d2d2e06887602cb","tid":729743,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"黎緊有排跌<br />\n買少少熊仔賺下零用算啦<br />\n1千幾百蝕左唔怕肉痛<br />\n輸過就會成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}